### R - search hamlets by name (accent-insensitive)
### get all hamlets (no keyword)
GET {{uri}}?page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### search by name with accents
GET {{uri}}?keyword=Th%C3%B4n%20B%E1%BB%91n&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### search by name without accents (should still match "Thôn Bốn")
GET {{uri}}?keyword=thon%20bon&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### search with communeId filter
GET {{uri}}?communeId=0f1c0a3a-3c3c-4f33-8c24-7a7c0d6a0006&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### search with type filter (VILLAGE)
GET {{uri}}?type=VILLAGE&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### search with type filter (HAMLET)
GET {{uri}}?type=HAMLET&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json

### search with keyword, communeId, and type filter
GET {{uri}}?keyword=thon%20bon&communeId=0f1c0a3a-3c3c-4f33-8c24-7a7c0d6a0006&type=HAMLET&page=0&size=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Accept: application/json
